This is a Japanese mustard spinach cultivar bred for exceptional versatility and productivity in confined spaces. ‘Metro-Spin’ combines the mild, sweet flavour of spinach with the robust texture and nutritional punch of the mustard family, creating a highly adaptable green that thrives on frequent harvesting and produces a continuous yield of large, tender leaves.

